This file is part of sbf (SConsBuildFramework).

Introduction
============

The version number of sbf could be found in file VERSION.
sbf, a shortcut for SConsBuildFrameWork is a build system construct using SCons to compile and link c++ projects.
For more information on this library, see the subdirectory doc or the online documentation available at 
http://code.google.com/p/sbf/w/list.

The NEWS file tersely lists features that are new in this release.

